The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | In the City
                                                                                                                       7                                                                                      IN THE CITY
                  
	Mohun Bagan have called Australian central defender of African origin Okwy Okonkwo for a trial. Presently playing for Australian club Western Knights SC, Okwy, if selected, will be recruited under the Asian quota.       
	He will be arriving on Monday. The club, on Saturday, roped in Punjab stopper Harpreet Singh.                 
	 Riya Dutta will meet Suparna Bhattacharya in the womens singles final of the All-Bengal BBS Table Tennis Championship, organised by Bhowanipore Bayam Sangha. In the girls final, Riya will face Survi Patwari.                                                                                                                                                      
